eNCA’s Dasen Thathiah just had to catch a ride with Mngoma to hear it for himself. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A self-taught tenor – who works for Uber has become a hit on social media. Passenger Kim Davey posted a video of Durbanite Menzi Mngoma, entertaining her on a trip recently. Mngoma said to eNCA, “I told her how about listening to myself. So she’s like no it’s fine, you can go for a shot and then I was just doing it light and then she was so excited to hear me singing and then she posted it on Facebook.” eNCA's Dasen Thathiah caught a ride with Mngoma to hear it for himself. Watch the full interview above